            <article class="lp-show-card">
                <span class="lp-show-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">edit_note</span></span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Post yozing</h3>
                    <p>O'qigan kitobingiz haqida taassurotlaringizni yozing, muqova rasmini biriktiring va
                        yulduzcha bilan baholang. Postingiz kuzatuvchilaringiz tasmasida paydo bo'ladi.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lp-show-card">
                <span class="lp-show-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">chat_bubble</span></span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Muhokama qiling</h3>
                    <p>Har bir postga yoqtirish bosing va izoh qoldiring. Yoqqan kitoblar atrofida
                        jonli suhbat va tavsiyalar tug'iladi.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="lp-show-card">
                <span class="lp-show-icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">format_quote</span></span>
                <div>
                    <h3>Iqtibos saqlang</h3>
                    <p>Kitobdagi eng yoqqan satrni chiroyli iqtibos kartochkasiga aylantiring — muallif va
                        kitob nomi bilan. Shaxsiy iqtiboslar to'plamingizni yig'ing.</p>
                </div>
            </article>
