                <li><span class="material-symbols-outlined">calendar_month</span> Har oy yangi davr — 1-kundan oxirgi kungacha</li>
                <li><span class="material-symbols-outlined">trending_up</span> Jonli reyting — yetakchilarni real vaqtda kuzating</li>
                <li><span class="material-symbols-outlined">workspace_premium</span> Oy oxirida g'oliblar tantanali e'lon qilinadi</li>
                <li><span class="material-symbols-outlined">redeem</span> 1-, 2- va 3-o'rin uchun kitob sovg'asi</li>
